<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <%- include('../partials/head'); %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <div>
        <div class="main__container">
          <div class="main__header">
            <h1
              style="
                border: none;
                background-color: transparent;
                margin: 0px;
                padding: 0px;
              "
            >
              Binary Search Tree
            </h1>
            <h5 style="display: flex; margin-top: 8px; color: grey">
              <span style="color: #000000">Duration: </span> &nbsp;5 minutes
            </h5>
          </div>

          <div class="main__question">
            <h4>
              Problem:
              <span style="color: grey">
                Construct Full Binary Tree using its Preorder traversal and
                Preorder traversal of its mirror tree
              </span>
            </h4>
            <h3><%= assignmentID %></h3>
            <h3><%= modelID %></h3>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0px">
              Given two arrays that represent Preorder traversals of a full
              binary tree and its mirror tree, we need to write a program to
              construct the binary tree using these two Preorder traversals. A
              Full Binary Tree is a binary tree where every node has either 0 or
              2 children. Note: It is not possible to construct a general binary
              tree using these two traversal. But we can create a full binary
              tree using the above traversals without any ambiguity. For more
              details refer to this article.
            </p>
            <h4 style="margin-top: 20px">Test Cases:</h4>
            <div id="test-cases"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="main__editorContainer">
            <div class="main__editorControls">
              <div style="margin-left: 100px">
                <img
                  height="70"
                  width="70"
                  src="/src/img/code.png"
                  alt="Code-image"
                />
              </div>

              <button
                style="
                  width: 120px;
                  margin: 10px;
                  margin-left: 30px;
                  background-color: green;
                  color: #000000;
                  height: 50px;
                "
              >
                Run
              </button>

              <button
                onclick="save()"
                style="
                  width: 120px;
                  margin: 10px;
                  background-color: red;
                  color: #000000;
                  height: 50px;
                "
              >
                Submit
              </button>
            </div>

            <div class="main__editor">
              <div class="editors">
                <div class="editor-column">
                  <div class="editor" id="source-editor"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="main__console-output">
              <div id="output-window"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer'); %> <%- include('../partials/scripts'); %>
  </body>
</html>
